name: NWEthernetChannel.State
desc: States indicating whether an Ethernet channel is able to send and receive frames.

items.name: case setup
items.desc: The channel has been initialized but not started.

items.name: case waiting(NWError)
items.desc: The channel is waiting for its interface to become available.

items.name: case preparing
items.desc: The channel is registering with the interface.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: The channel is able to send and receive Ethernet frames.

items.name: case failed(NWError)
items.desc: The channel has encountered a fatal error.
